title: Got an S, didn't receive a chest

embed.description: Every game is a story; visit the new League of Legends match history to check out how this one ends and share your own!

body:
So I got an S-, never received a chest. Haven't received a chest for a Malphite game inawhile, profile shows I still have 4 available. 

May I have the chest I earned, please?

Thank you,

Porro

replies.body: Hey Porro!  I checked into this for you and it looks like you already received a mastery chest for Malphite a while ago.  Your champion pool in the client will show you if you already received one for that season.  Let me know if that clears things up!
